reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This was so unique and a great price. My grand daughter loves it. It holds so much, the zipper seems great and the material is easily washable

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I saw this on an influencer’s YouTube and was needing a makeup bag. This is great-holds a lot, opens super wide so you don’t have to pull everything out, has smaller pockets inside, and looks nice. The quality may not be amazing but the price is great and I usually have to replace my makeup bags ever so often anyway.I probably wouldn’t recommend this for an “on the go” bag (airplane, car, etc.) because of how wide it opens and things may fall out.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The perfect makeup bag! Compact yet sturdy. Will hold its shape well without collapsing but doesn't take up too much room. I'm obsessed with how small it appears when it's zipped but how big/easily accessible it is and how much it holds when open! My mom had this bag before me and I couldn't believe how cheap it was once she told me. Ordered immediately -- no regrets!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Love this makeup bag
reviews.reviewText: I almost rated this a 5 but hesitated since I want to take it to Europe this summer before a final review. I have so many makeup bags that I hate for one reason or another. This one has separate sections, a zipper interior section. I was concerned that when you zipper the bag up everything would fall together to one big mess. Not so far!! Lots of room and I thing will fit neatly in a corner if my carryon. Fingers crossed.

reviews.reviewText: The size of bag is great and the design is exactly what I wanted but the material on the inside is very cheaply made and the zipper on the middle pocket fell off on day two.
